{"tid":1192650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"00後嘅我決定去返送中遊行","createTime":"2019-06-08T14:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T02:50:25.000Z","uid":211074,"like":55,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"648b71bd32d2ee6d16528597352cef7e7ad081e8","tid":1192650,"uid":211074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T14:09:32.000Z","msg":"我知喺連登公開自己係00後等於自願俾人批鬥<br />\n<br />\n我係喺香港出世喺香港長大喺香港讀書 我好明白我擁有嘅一切 都係前人嘅努力 留低俾我<br />\n<br />\n法治 人權 言論自由 新聞自由 集會自由 廉潔 呢啲嘅核心價值 如果唔係前人留低 我邊可以因為我係香港人嘅身份而感到自豪<br />\n<br />\n雨傘革命對我來講係一個轉捩點 嗰陣時仲讀緊初中嘅我 勾起左我對時事嘅熱誠 眼見香港法治倒退 我點可以任由一班賣港賊 將前人嘅努力付諸流水<br />\n<br />\n我唔想我曾經最愛嘅香港 變成我最討厭嘅大陸<br />\n<br />\n無論你係咩年代出世 都要企出嚟 捍衛香港！<br />\n<br />\n致港豬：聰明到不願意碰政治的人，就注定要被比較笨的人統治。<br />\nThose who are too smart to engage in politics are condemned to being governed by those who are dumber. <br />\n<br />\n柏拉圖 Plato<br />\n<br />\n利申 仲考緊試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b9c8bc0a4c512de40682fa0665385a700d4d5d","tid":1192650,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T14:09:58.000Z","msg":"Thank you!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>槍口一致對外！<br />\n<br />\n不要分化！不要懷疑隊友！<br />\n<br />\n有人被捕立即群擁而上集體救援！<br />\n<br />\n勿比機會警犬單獨拉走同伴！<br />\n<br />\n一切行動必須群體出發！ <br />\n<br />\nStick Together Team! 不要落單！<br />\n<br />\n6.9 GOGOGO!</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>唔衝嘅人幫手拖住篤灰狗 <br />\n<br />\n衝嘅巴繼續上前！<br />\n<br />\n齊心！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be402483bf68dc0a3e25150979875c8ffc8728d","tid":1192650,"uid":211074,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r